{
  "stem": "21308.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in 1938 November, Munich had just taken place in 1938.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That would be September, I think, Munich was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was near Aldershot with my regiment and we, in fact, had just been re-equipped with guns and we'd just lost our horses and we'd just been re-equipped with mechanical transport.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were new boys all the way around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, that's when-- that-- we would have been near Aldershot, a little village called Ewshot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was all in the Aldershot command.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think people were very angry about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- it-- it made it quite clear that war was very likely.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "War was very likely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was nothing we could do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was nothing we could do about it because we were just ordinary soldiers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as I said to your earlier, what did you did?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You did as you were told.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] --I think it be a good idea to mention Munich because the Munich Agreement, Hitler thought he got everybody on toast, and-- but he didn't cater with the British attitude.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think the British attitude was after Munich, Chamberlain had done his best to preserve peace.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Some people weren't very pleased with that because they felt that he had acted in a manner which he shouldn't have done.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they're entitled to do that in a democracy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I know that in Munich, at the time of Munich, we were in no fit state to go to war.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "As I've just told you, we'd just been getting new guns and we'd just been converted from animal draft to mechanical draft.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In actual fact, we'd just received our first wireless set-- field wireless sets.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were in no fit state whatsoever to go to war.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
